message.html_body:
To ensure a smooth and hassle-free experience for your upcoming visit, we kindly request you to upload your insurance details. Having this information ahead of time helps us to expedite the billing process and ensures that you receive the full benefits of your coverage.

Steps for Uploading Insurance Details:

  1. Locate Your Insurance Card: Please have your insurance card ready. This contains all the necessary information we need.
  2. Access the Insurance Section: In the bottom, navigate to next.
  3. Upload Photos of Your Card: Use your phone to take clear pictures of the front and back of your insurance card. Make sure all details are legible.


Thanks!
message.subject: Upload Your Insurance Details
